## Step 2: Identify any fixed asset additions

Total depreciation: 45,754.08 + 45,755.86 = 91,509.94

## Step 4: Calculate the ending fixed assets net value
Since there were no additions to fixed assets, the ending value is simply:

= 8,000,000.00 - 91,509.94
= 7,908,490.06
